    "body": "This is a first, crude attempt at modularizing NMP, mostly meant to ignite some discussion. I chose to modularize the keepalive module as it is fairly simple and straightforward. I plan on modularizing two other components before calling this feature-complete : \r\n\r\n- [ ] Handshaking\r\n- [x] Ping\r\n\r\nOpen questions : \r\n\r\n- Should we provide a way to detach a module from NMP ?\r\n- Should we actually standardize modules, or should they be kept internal ?",
